  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Modifies quorum requirements and repeals condominium association board election proxy voting.  Authorizes the Real Estate Commission to take certain actions in response to alleged or actual violations of rules or laws relating to condominium association board elections.  Imposes certain duties and obligations on condominium association directors concerning election processes.  Clarifies the conditions for a valid condominium association board election.  Substitutes certain requirements for written affidavits with requirements for written certification in relation to access to association documents."
    }
  ],
